data.description: **OPTION TO ASSUME CURRENT FHA LOAN AT A 3.25% INTEREST RATE!** Welcome to The Narrows— conveniently located right off of Hwy 280 which means you'll have access to nearby parks, restaurants, Oak Mountain Schools…AND is just a 10-min drive to Grandview Medical & the Summit Shopping! This floor plan offers MAIN-LEVEL LIVING with a spacious great room with a gas fireplace & large bedrooms. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen, complete with modern appliances, ample cabinet space, a breakfast nook, & a formal dining room off of the kitchen. The primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet & an en-suite bathroom with a relaxing soaking tub, separate shower, & double vanity. The 2 additional bedrooms include BRAND NEW CARPET and offer plenty of room for family/guests. Outside, the covered back patio is perfect for hosting parties in any weather! This home features 4-sides brick and a 2-car garage for parking and/or storage.
